">599J強制檢測途徑</span></strong>：<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=aa78a1ab\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（名單：<a href=\"http://www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=ad14b15a\" target=\"_blank\">www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a>）[中資]<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，以及樣本收集點及時間：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=aa78a1ab\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（名單：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=8480c73d\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a>）<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。</span>"},{"pid":"28f87f4e2a80bb47c4e597e65dae0d597ab59f59","tid":2501232,"uid":337428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84a7a9f9ee531a0b22372101e456a45fdff8b280","tid":2501232,"uid":282626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=